<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING ANSWERS</h1><h3>Q1: Can you tell me about your typical morning routine?</h3><p>Ans: When do you wake up ?.
I wake up at 6.0 am 
How do you feel ?. I feel sleepy.
What do you do in your bedroom ?.
I do my bed and do my hair. 
What do you do in your bathroom ?.
I brush teeth (i:) , wash my face and shower.
What do you do in kitchen ?.
I do cooking. 
What do you have your breakfast ?. 
I have rice, ommelet vegetable and pork for breakfast.
What do you have for drink. 
I drink a cup of water, orange juice.
Why do you have orange juicy ?.
because orange juicy is delicious and healthy.
do + N: dọn và làm. </p><hr><h3>Q2: What do you have for breakfast and how do you go to school?</h3><p>Ans: How do you go to school ?.
I go to school by my motorbike. 
Why motorbike ?.
Because school is near my house. 
How far ? 
It is a kilometre. 
How long ?
only five minutes driving (lái xe).</p><hr><h3>Q3: How do you cook rice?</h3><p>Ans: How do you cook rice?
Wash: First I wash rice (vo gạo).
Pour: And I pour water and rice in the rice cooker (nồi cơm điện).
Wait: Finally, I wait 30 minutes.</p><hr><h3>Q4: Do you like reading books? Where and Why?</h3><p>Ans: Do you like reading books ?
Yes, i am book lover. 
Where do you read book ?. 
(i read books in library at school. sometimes i read books in my bedroom at home).
Why do you read in the library ?. 
It is near my house -> it is two kilometres (metres) -> and only 5 five minutes driving. 
-> Library has many books. I can find (= look for: tìm thấy) favourite (yêu thích) book.
find what i need (tìm thấy thứ mình cần).    
Why do you love Reading books ?.
Because it is my hobby. I feel relaxed.
Do you like to read alone or read with friend ?.
I love reading books with my friends because more people more fun. I can share book with friends </p><hr><h3>Q5: Do you like shopping? When and Where?</h3><p>Ans: Do you like shopping? 
When do you go shopping ?. I go shopping in my free time. 
When is your free time ?. I have free time at the weekend.
Why at the weekend but not other days ?. because i go to school from Monday to Friday.
Where do you go shopping ?. 
I go shopping at the supermarket. 
Why do you go shopping supermarket ?.
Because supermarket is near my house. It is two kilometres. only ten minutes driving.
Why do you go shopping at supermarket but not on small shop ?.
Supermarket has many products. I can look for favourite product.
products (n): sản phẩm = items 
</p><hr><h3>Q6: Do you like walking? Where do you go?</h3><p>Ans: Do you like walking ? Yes, i am a walking lover
Where do you go walking ?
I go walking at the park. because park is near my house. It is five kilometres, only 10 minutes walking. 
When do you go walking ?.
in my free time. I have free time at the weekend because i go to school from Monday to Friday.
Why do you love walking ?.
-> because it is hobby. I feel relaxed.
-> and it is healthy.
What does the park have ?.
The park is very beautiful. The park has many trees, flowers and a lake (n): cái hồ.
Are there many people in the park ?.
I think the park has not many people. It is quite and peaceful. 
quite (adj): yên tĩnh
peaceful (adj): yên bình
What do you usually do in the park ?.
I usually go walking in the park, sit (ngồi) on the chair (ghế) and read books.  












</p><hr><h3>Q7: Do you like dancing?</h3><p>Ans: Do you like dancing ?. 
Yes, i am dacing lover. 
Where do you dance ?
I dance in the ballet room at school. 
sometimes i dance in my bedroom at home.
When do you dance ?.
I dance in my free time. I have free time at the weekend because i go to school from Monday to Friday. 
Why do you love dancing ?.
It is hobby. I feel relaxed
and it is good for health and exciting. 
Do you love singing ?.
What is your favourite song ?.
My favourite song is "love story" by (bởi) taylor swift singer. 
artist, singer (n).
What is your kind of music ?. (pop, ballad, rock).
My favourite  kind of music is ballad. 















</p><hr></body></html>